706438f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ralph Avenue - Bergen Street
706438f-a.text:
Ralph Avenue, north from Bergen Street. Buildings on the
west side of the avenue are being razed to mke way for the erec-
tion of the Kingsborough Houses--a public, low-cost housing center.
June 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
